To overcome these challenges, current research focuses on incorporating textual information available in the KGs to improve the KG embeddings, boost performance in downstream tasks, and to support ILP.
The latent representation is learned from textual information using a variety of encoding models such as linear models, convolutional models, recurrent neural models, and LLMs and studied in [lu2020utilizing,pan2023unifying]. 
In this work, we focus only on LLM-based methods.